{"tid":1248783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"謹記，陽光與媒體是我們最大的後盾","createTime":"2019-06-21T14:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T15:03:08.000Z","uid":29132,"like":119,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c3f750e9a558214d64268a044c87acae370989a5","tid":1248783,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:15:52.000Z","msg":"警總，不能衝。適時要退，敵進我退，小心，不受傷，不被捕。<br />\n<br />\n長期戰爭，寧圍兩日晨，不圍一日晚，夜晚狗開始吠，社會注目係我地嘅保障，安全最重要。<br />\n<br />\n謹記，長期戰，我地唔可以一晚建立新制度，權始終係警犬到，我地要做長期不合作運動，不在於一時。"},{"pid":"2291bd14de6ee5568222637931b26d6a74287ffe","tid":1248783,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:16:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"54fca792faae2fbac300d3141d2d6eee5c924192","tid":1248783,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:17:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6a4ad10278af630c86a9b6d8ad4862657a3545f4","tid":1248783,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:18:03.000Z","msg":"支持 烈士遺言 我地唔係暴徒<br />\n<br />\n我地唔洗自眨身價同佢鬥賤架!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認清目標 聚焦醫警濫權<br />\n<br />\n修例係撤回定停止已經唔係重點<br />\n<br />\n今日圍完 應該盡早散 僵持不下無意思<br />\n<br />\n國際人權組織已經出左報告 今晚有意外就前功盡廢了<br />\n<br />\n手足辛苦完 應該到宣傳組出場<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位耐心睇完"},{"pid":"ecd7acd4c38c99eed38a79ecf5aac0f417cd3ce6","tid":1248783,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:18:18.000Z","msg":"Ag is"},{"pid":"6a7c1d34d95a8d67392ea270462787ebc4ec284b","tid":1248783,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:18:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冷靜，唔好衝，注意時機隨時撤退，be water my friend</span></span>"},{"pid":"36f472b7cd7e5182fa387f64833482dcd9d10d06","tid":1248783,"uid":266654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:19:13.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"25f340ad7074600e29923f7b6e223eb0ce8d6c77","tid":1248783,"uid":214984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc